item.title: PRINTING
item.dc:creator: cstory
item.content:encoded:
Cstory is your print specialists … <!--more-->
Printing couldn't be easier with us. Our extensive range of great value products makes us the perfect choice for all your print needs.

item.title: WEBSITE DESIGN
item.dc:creator: cstory
item.content:encoded:
We have extensive digital expertise … <!--more-->
that can help you get discovered in a crowded marketplace, and convert browsers into buyers.
It’s no longer enough just to have great design and a good marketing plan. A brand that’s going to succeed is one that has a solid digital marketing strategy – and the tools to support it.
At Cstory we look at all of your branding and marketing elements and how they can all work together to enhance the user experience. We know the value of reaching your customers and prospects across several channels, and how to increase the impact of that multi-channel hit.
Our digital solutions include website design and development, mobile apps, digital and email campaigns.
We create digital solutions that get users clicking and sales sizzling.

item.title: PACKAGING
item.dc:creator: cstory
item.content:encoded:
It’s not just about first impressions … <!--more-->
It’s about lasting impressions. Like the clothes you wear, the package you put forward says a lot about you and your brand. Jars, boxes, lids, crates, labels, pouches, you name it…it all tell a story. These all touch points with your customer and opportunities to get them to love your brand and recommend it to others.
Cstory specialises in creating powerful packaging that engages the consumer and smokes the competition. Over the years we have created exceptional packaging solutions for a wide range of clients across New Zealand, Australia, US, Korea and China.

item.title: GRAPHIC DESIGN
item.dc:creator: cstory
item.content:encoded:
CStory believes … <!--more-->
A strong brand, supposedly an intangible asset, can easily become a company’s single most valuable asset. Strong brands cut through the clutter, differentiate the product and add immeasurable value. It is the element of your business that communicates credibility and instils trust. So it is vital that you get the design of your brand right.
Cstory specialises are creating unique brands that help our clients get noticed.
We take all of the values and features that make up your identity and translate them into visual elements you and your customers will love.
Through strategic thinking and considered design, we can help create something new or we can refresh a brand that needs reinvigorating.
